= pmAjaxLoadPlugin =

Displays an image while the page is loading.

== Installation ==

  * Install the plugin

    {{{
      svn export http://svn.symfony-project.com/plugins/pmAjaxLoadPlugin/trunk pmAjaxLoadPlugin
    }}}

  * Clear the cache

    {{{
      symfony cc
    }}}

  * Use it in a template

    {{{
      <?php use_helper("AjaxLoad") ?>

      <?php ajax_load() // this uses the default settings ?>
    }}}

  * You can pass options to ajax_load functions, such as:

    * title
    * icon
    * help
    * background-color
    * opacity
